{"tid":482134,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"全球近 500 個知名網站暗中紀錄用家鍵盤操作行為","createTime":"2017-11-28T01:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T10:26:03.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"13831270efe09f573ec39625c2cc5ebf1ec6385b","tid":482134,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:32:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">這些網站包括：Telegraph、路透社、CBS News、Samsung、Microsoft、Adobe、ASUS、League of Lengends 等。<br />\n<br />\n完整名單：<br />\n<a href=\"https://webtransparency.cs.princeton.edu/no_boundaries/session_replay_sites.html#methodology\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebtransparency.cs.princeton.edu%2Fno_boundaries%2Fsession_replay_sites.html%23methodology&d=qd1qbqGz5wfWBr0zsx1ultibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=46799b8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://webtransparency.cs.princeton.edu/no_boundaries/session_replay_sites.html#methodology</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1950000/1954366/keyboard_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1950000%2F1954366%2Fkeyboard_1024_1024.jpg&h=81346cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1954366/全球近%20500%20個知名網站暗中紀錄用家鍵盤操作行為\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1954366%2F%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%BF%91%2520500%2520%E5%80%8B%E7%9F%A5%E5%90%8D%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E6%9A%97%E4%B8%AD%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B6%E9%8D%B5%E7%9B%A4%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA&d=qd1qbqGz5wfWBr0zsx1ultibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ee2a741c\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1954366/全球近%20500%20個知名網站暗中紀錄用家鍵盤操作行為</a></div>"},{"pid":"cba4250924f10d010494baf169f52004ab523bf3","tid":482134,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:33:50.000Z","msg":"互聯網已成為生活不可分割的一部份，但隨之來，也出現種種侵犯私隱的問題。早前，美國普林斯頓大學的資訊技術政策中心（Center for Information Technology Policy，CITP）便公布一項研究報告，調查全球 5 萬個最多流量的網站，發現當中近 500 個，會利用 Session replay（紀錄行為重播），將用戶的使用行徑紀錄，並傳送到第三方伺服器上。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1950000/1954366/user_replay_automated_redaction_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1950000%2F1954366%2Fuser_replay_automated_redaction_600.jpg&h=6f92714a&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1bb73ec6e777add2f6495ceb9a84902331d3512f","tid":482134,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:34:31.000Z","msg":"所謂 Session replay，意思是指網站會紀錄使用者的行為，包含：鍵盤敲擊、滑鼠移動、瀏覽行為、所停留的網頁內容等，原因通常為了進行各種分析，改善使用用者的體驗，又或用於各種研究。CITP 因應 7 間提供 Session replay 服務的公司，包括：FullStory、Hotjar、Yandex、Smartlook 等，再根據 Alexa 的流量排行榜，調查前 5 萬個網站，發現其中 482 個，有使用相關服務。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1950000/1954366/user_replay_bonobos_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1950000%2F1954366%2Fuser_replay_bonobos_600.jpg&h=f38cf2f0&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"76756d7a55dcbd6be5d65c551fcca8077d7bbf20","tid":482134,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:36:04.000Z","msg":"d公司有回應未？"},{"pid":"7f7152e62970553313b849508ade6b544214f021","tid":482134,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:36:09.000Z","msg":"按理說，提供 Session replay 服務的供應商，應該要過濾使用者輸入的各種機密資訊。不過測試發現，部分仍然可紀錄使用者的密碼、用戶身份資料、信用卡後 4 碼、醫療狀況等，當中有 3 間供應商，在傳送重播內容時，更使用的是未加密的 HTTP 協定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。在 7 間供應商之中，亦只有一間，允許使用者關閉追蹤與紀錄功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。用家即使用廣告攔截軟體、瀏覽器內的防追蹤保護功能，亦不一定能完全阻擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1950000/1954366/user_replay_lenovo_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1950000%2F1954366%2Fuser_replay_lenovo_600.jpg&h=5e8e84fb&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c4eb2830ec3b6b26802062d6665e2ceafeb1e7c1","tid":482134,"uid":53223,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:37:57.000Z","msg":"邊度都會監控嫁啦"},{"pid":"5378dc3e5c6a36e5c8bdaa1d812caa5b61452c2e","tid":482134,"uid":69484,"like":3,"dislike":29,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:39:54.000Z","msg":"屌 你地d小人物驚死被人爆資料<br />\n一黎 真係出事告到破產都得<br />\n二黎 科技發展難免啦 <br />\n唔駛大驚小怪wo"},{"pid":"015417eb39d0d5f88be262dc8b4e31ca014d024f","tid":482134,"uid":121721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751d3c27b390236ec449f1973355280eb6de2abe","tid":482134,"uid":158660,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:48:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13ab5a129d6e98c118dedebb72675d38bd595e09","tid":482134,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:50:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Microsoft都有？<br />\n咁我開OneDrive上下載同女朋友啲性感相咪俾人睇晒？屌！！！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc660d07f394d4a933096651366f5ea7d57c796","tid":482134,"uid":73231,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"其實做 UX 研究同埋 Lansing page optimization 係常用手法<br />\n應該個網頁terms of use 有寫會咁做<br />\n差在你有冇睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMarketers 除咗呢啲仲知你哋好多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3635ae114cd094c774df4f00c91433e4274d15a","tid":482134,"uid":13718,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"冇用HTTPS 先係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28cd0a5d0cf0beb8335194f58815c6a0a24639d","tid":482134,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:31:27.000Z","msg":"宜家法例係d 資料可以trace 到某個人先算個人資料，keylogger 出的資料算唔算個人資料？"},{"pid":"0b7b7f617fcbbfd645c9beb0932aeed22b784503","tid":482134,"uid":61249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 你地d小人物驚死被人爆資料<br />\n一黎 真係出事告到破產都得<br />\n二黎 科技發展難免啦 <br />\n唔駛大驚小怪wo</blockquote><br />\n比人爆唔係重點<br />\n重點係咁log 法係咪合乎道德"},{"pid":"60917e0f960a3a89799ffb544443c1938a59e4e4","tid":482134,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:34:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家法例係d 資料可以trace 到某個人先算個人資料，keylogger 出的資料算唔算個人資料？</blockquote><br />\nkey log 左個 email string 同另一組 string 算唔算偷資料"},{"pid":"9ef6d6ad00b5d611e54da9e88e6ad9c4e2389d0c","tid":482134,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宜家法例係d 資料可以trace 到某個人先算個人資料，keylogger 出的資料算唔算個人資料？</blockquote><br />\nkey log 左個 email string 同另一組 string 算唔算偷資料</blockquote><br />\n有時打頭兩隻字之後auto complete 個email, keylogger 都未必replay得番。所以我覺得係灰色位"},{"pid":"64359a069dc90eb675a810766e87ab0b442b5080","tid":482134,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"